# fusion-gotchas.lap

[gotchas]
- Units are always centimeters internally, regardless of UI settings
- Always check return values for None -- operations fail silently
- Use design.designType = ParametricDesignType before parametric features
- Input objects must be fully configured before calling .add()
- Sketch profiles only available after geometry is fully closed
- Point3D.create() takes cm, not mm or inches
- Collections are 0-indexed, use .item(i) or [i]
- CoilFeatures is read-only — coils cannot be created via the API despite CoilFeatureInput existing

[meta]
api: Autodesk Fusion
lang: python
namespace: adsk.core, adsk.fusion, adsk.cam
import: import adsk.core, adsk.fusion, adsk.cam

# fusion-core.lap

[types]
AppearanceSourceTypes: MaterialAppearanceSource | BodyAppearanceSource | OccurrenceAppearanceSource | FaceAppearanceSource | OverrideAppearanceSource
BoundingBoxEntityTypes: AllEntitiesBoundingBoxEntityType | SolidBRepBodyBoundingBoxEntityType | SurfaceBodyBoundingBoxEntityType | MeshBodyBoundingBoxEntityType | SketchBoundingBoxEntityType | ConstructionBoundingBoxEntityType
CameraTypes: OrthographicCameraType | PerspectiveCameraType | PerspectiveWithOrthoFacesCameraType
ChainedCurveOptions: noChainedCurves | connectedChainedCurves | tangentChainedCurves | openEdgesChainedCurves | tangentAndOpenEdgesChainedCurves
CloseError: CloseCancelledError
Curve2DTypes: Line2DCurveType | Arc2DCurveType | Circle2DCurveType | Ellipse2DCurveType | EllipticalArc2DCurveType | InfiniteLine2DCurveType | NurbsCurve2DCurveType | Polyline2DCurveType
Curve3DTypes: Line3DCurveType | Arc3DCurveType | Circle3DCurveType | Ellipse3DCurveType | EllipticalArc3DCurveType | InfiniteLine3DCurveType | NurbsCurve3DCurveType | Polyline3DCurveType
DeleteMeError: ParameterReferencedByOtherParameterError
DistanceUnits: MillimeterDistanceUnits | CentimeterDistanceUnits | MeterDistanceUnits | InchDistanceUnits | FootDistanceUnits | YardDistanceUnits | MicronDistanceUnits | HectometerDistanceUnits | MileDistanceUnits | MilDistanceUnits | NauticalMileDistanceUnits
ExpressionError: CyclicParameterReferenceError
FutureStates: ProcessingFutureState | FinishedFutureState | FailedFutureState
GenericErrors: Ok | UnexpectedError | InternalValidationError | BadApiCallError | UnderlyingObjectDeletedError | OperationFailed | ExpressionError | InvalidGeometryError | ClassSpecificError | FunctionSpecificError
LineStylePatterns: continuousLineStylePattern | centerLineStylePattern | dashedLineStylePattern | dotLineStylePattern | hiddenLineStylePattern | phantomLineStylePattern | tracksLineStylePattern | zigzagLineStylePattern
LinearDiameterDimensionPreferenceTypes: DefaultLinearDiameterDimensionPreferenceType | PreferLinearDiameterDimensionPreferenceType | AvoidLinearDiameterDimensionPreferenceType
MachineAnglePreferences: MachineAngleNoPreference | MachineAnglePreferNegative | MachineAnglePreferPositive
MassUnits: GramMassUnits | KilogramMassUnits | PoundMassUnits | OunceMassUnits | TonMassUnits | SlugMassUnits
MaterialDisplayUnits: MetricStandardDisplayUnits | MetricMKSDisplayUnits | MetricMMNSDisplayUnits | MetricCGSDisplayUnits | MetricUMNSDisplayUnits | EnglishStandardDisplayUnits | EnglishInchDisplayUnits | EnglishFootDisplayUnits
MeshUnits: CentimeterMeshUnit | MillimeterMeshUnit | MeterMeshUnit | InchMeshUnit | FootMeshUnit
MultiAxisSingularityLinearizeMethod: MultiAxisSingularityLinearize_Linear | MultiAxisSingularityLinearize_Rotary
NurbsSurfaceProperties: OpenNurbsSurface | ClosedNurbsSurface | PeriodicNurbsSurface | RationalNurbsSurface
OpenDocumentError: DocumentNotFoundError
ParameterValueTypes: NumericParameterValueType | TextParameterValueType
PointContainment: PointInsidePointContainment | PointOnPointContainment | PointOutsidePointContainment | UnknownPointContainment
ProgrammingLanguages: PromptForLanguage | PythonProgrammingLanguage | CPPProgramminglanguage | TypeScriptProgrammingLanguage
SaveLocalErrors: SaveCancelledSaveLocalError | DiskFullSaveLocalError | FileReadOnlySaveLocalError
ScriptSourceLocations: AppStoreScriptSourceLocation | OtherInstalledScriptSourceLocation | UserDefinedScriptSourceLocation | InternalScriptSourceLocation | SamplesScriptSourceLocation | LinkedScriptSourceLocation
SketchCurveConstructionStates: ToggleSketchCurveConstructionState | ConstructionSketchCurveConstructionState | NormalSketchCurveConstructionState
SketchLineCenterlineStates: ToggleSketchLineCenterlineState | CenterlineSketchLineCenterlineState | NormalSketchLineCenterlineState
UnitSystems: CustomUnitSystem | MillimeterGramUnitSystem | CentimeterGramUnitSystem | MeterKilogramUnitSystem | InchOunceUnitSystem | FootPoundUnitSystem
ValueInputError: ValueNotOfTypeError
VectorError: ZeroLengthVectorError

